setAccountingCurrency.t.sol
├── when caller is not the module's safe
│  └── it should revert with UnauthorizedCaller
└── when caller is the module's safe
   ├── given price data is not registered for provided currency
   │  └── it should revert with PriceFeedRouteNotRegistered
   └── given price data is registered for provided currency
      └── it should set the accounting currency in the contract storage
